      "id": "path_caveat_content",
      "x": 1051.921875,
      "y": 1474.7890625,
      "width": 496.2890625,
      "height": 41.25,
      "text": "Infra prod: apps/infrastructure/*/overlays/prod-tenant/<tenant>/\nWorkload prod: apps/workloads/*/overlays/prod/tenant/<tenant>/\nNote: directory presence = deployment target. Omit dir = no deploy to tenant.",
      "originalText": "Infra prod: apps/infrastructure/*/overlays/prod-tenant/<tenant>/\nWorkload prod: apps/workloads/*/overlays/prod/tenant/<tenant>/\nNote: directory presence = deployment target. Omit dir = no deploy to tenant.",
